## Theme & Styling
- Always use Toyota Gazoo Racing color scheme
- Primary: #EB0A1E (Red), Secondary: #000000 (Black)
- Use Tailwind CSS v4 with @theme directive
- Follow established component patterns

## Architecture
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript for type safety
- API helpers in lib/api/
- Modal components for forms
- Consistent error handling and loading states

## File Organization
- Components in app/[feature]/components/
- API helpers in lib/api/
- Use kebab-case for file names
- Keep related files together

## Code Standards
- Use "use client" for interactive components
- Include proper TypeScript interfaces
- Add loading states to all async operations
- Use consistent error handling patterns